_:N9ad9c5bb5e4f4610be0ae50a8be2e7b5 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Nick Goodwin was appointed Chief Executive of <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-courts-and-tribunals-service\">HM Courts and Tribunals Service (HMCTS)</a> in March 2022.</p>\n\n<p>Before joining HMCTS, he was Chief Executive and Public Guardian in the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-public-guardian\">Office of the Public Guardian (OPG)</a> from July 2019. Before that, Nick was director for access to justice policy at the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice\">Ministry of Justice</a>.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
